{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/issues/72/comments/34785650.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat/issues/72#comment-34785650"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/issues/72.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 72, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{b6d52f9f-b070-41c0-807c-94af07ea375b}ts=1606789"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "sdformat", "full_name": "osrf/sdformat", "uuid": "{b6d52f9f-b070-41c0-807c-94af07ea375b}"}, "title": "Search for urdfdom_headers when USE_EXTERNAL_URDF=True"}, "content": {"raw": "Once we remove the built-in copy of urdfdom, I don't believe this will be an issue anymore.  Assigning to myself.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Once we remove the built-in copy of urdfdom, I don't believe this will be an issue anymore.  Assigning to myself.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-03-01T15:11:11.451362+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "clalancette", "uuid": "{02b311e1-297d-4232-89c4-5485d0a02911}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B02b311e1-297d-4232-89c4-5485d0a02911%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B02b311e1-297d-4232-89c4-5485d0a02911%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:ad6ed80b-ec66-45cb-9504-b1094a415b7f/048a0933-60ac-4910-a6a5-ed058bdea8eb/128"}}, "nickname": "clalancette", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:ad6ed80b-ec66-45cb-9504-b1094a415b7f"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 34785650}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/issues/72/comments/34785655.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat/issues/72#comment-34785655"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/issues/72.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 72, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{b6d52f9f-b070-41c0-807c-94af07ea375b}ts=1606789"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "sdformat", "full_name": "osrf/sdformat", "uuid": "{b6d52f9f-b070-41c0-807c-94af07ea375b}"}, "title": "Search for urdfdom_headers when USE_EXTERNAL_URDF=True"}, "content": {"raw": null, "markup": "markdown", "html": "", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-03-01T15:11:18.977772+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "clalancette", "uuid": "{02b311e1-297d-4232-89c4-5485d0a02911}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B02b311e1-297d-4232-89c4-5485d0a02911%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B02b311e1-297d-4232-89c4-5485d0a02911%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:ad6ed80b-ec66-45cb-9504-b1094a415b7f/048a0933-60ac-4910-a6a5-ed058bdea8eb/128"}}, "nickname": "clalancette", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:ad6ed80b-ec66-45cb-9504-b1094a415b7f"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 34785655}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/issues/72/comments/34802899.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat/issues/72#comment-34802899"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/issues/72.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 72, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{b6d52f9f-b070-41c0-807c-94af07ea375b}ts=1606789"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "sdformat", "full_name": "osrf/sdformat", "uuid": "{b6d52f9f-b070-41c0-807c-94af07ea375b}"}, "title": "Search for urdfdom_headers when USE_EXTERNAL_URDF=True"}, "content": {"raw": "I have the impression that this is not only an issue of sdformat, but also of the pkg-config generation of urdfdom . \n`sdformat` uses directly `urdfdom_headers`'s headers in [1], so it actually needs to search for `urdfdom_headers` . \nHowever, `urdfdom` uses `urdfdom_headers`'s in its public headers, so its pkg-config file would need to export the include\ndirs of  `urdfdom_headers`, similarly to how the CMake config packages does [2][3]. \nActually, as we need to use the CMake's `find_package` for #!/osrf/sdformat/pull-requests/324 , perhaps \nit could make sense to just stop using `pkg-config` to find `urdfdom` and just use CMake's `find_package`.\n\n[1] #!/osrf/sdformat/src/e5104282e829bc88e484bd2f63af86f3bde6bd42/src/parser_urdf.cc?at=default&fileviewer=file-view-default#parser_urdf.cc-25 . \n\n[2] https://github.com/ros/urdfdom/blob/master/CMakeLists.txt#L80\n\n[3] https://github.com/ros/urdfdom/blob/master/cmake/urdfdom-config.cmake.in#L25", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I have the impression that this is not only an issue of sdformat, but also of the pkg-config generation of urdfdom . \n<code>sdformat</code> uses directly <code>urdfdom_headers</code>'s headers in [1], so it actually needs to search for <code>urdfdom_headers</code> . \nHowever, <code>urdfdom</code> uses <code>urdfdom_headers</code>'s in its public headers, so its pkg-config file would need to export the include\ndirs of  <code>urdfdom_headers</code>, similarly to how the CMake config packages does [2][3]. \nActually, as we need to use the CMake's <code>find_package</code> for <a href=\"#!/osrf/sdformat/pull-requests/324\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">#!/osrf/sdformat/pull-requests/324</a> , perhaps \nit could make sense to just stop using <code>pkg-config</code> to find <code>urdfdom</code> and just use CMake's <code>find_package</code>.</p>\n<p>[1] <a href=\"#!/osrf/sdformat/src/e5104282e829bc88e484bd2f63af86f3bde6bd42/src/parser_urdf.cc?at=default&amp;fileviewer=file-view-default#parser_urdf.cc-25\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">#!/osrf/sdformat/src/e5104282e829bc88e484bd2f63af86f3bde6bd42/src/parser_urdf.cc?at=default&amp;fileviewer=file-view-default#parser_urdf.cc-25</a> . </p>\n<p>[2] <a href=\"https://github.com/ros/urdfdom/blob/master/CMakeLists.txt#L80\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://github.com/ros/urdfdom/blob/master/CMakeLists.txt#L80</a></p>\n<p>[3] <a href=\"https://github.com/ros/urdfdom/blob/master/cmake/urdfdom-config.cmake.in#L25\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://github.com/ros/urdfdom/blob/master/cmake/urdfdom-config.cmake.in#L25</a></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-03-02T08:25:48.987615+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Silvio Traversaro", "uuid": "{34f404cb-5642-4f27-a032-e04c7143d776}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B34f404cb-5642-4f27-a032-e04c7143d776%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B34f404cb-5642-4f27-a032-e04c7143d776%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:e1c3e6a0-9a64-4e5f-a668-feebc191c5b6/578caaa1-056c-45a2-8bf9-bee94c3bebef/128"}}, "nickname": "traversaro", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:e1c3e6a0-9a64-4e5f-a668-feebc191c5b6"}, "updated_on": "2017-03-02T09:11:15.275016+00:00", "type": "issue_comment", "id": 34802899}], "page": 1, "size": 3}